Package: HealthMarkers
Type: Package
Title: Toolkit for Clinical, Metabolic, and Cardiovascular Biomarker Calculations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sufyan", family = "Suleman",
           email = "sufyansuleman@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6612-6915"))
Description: Provides functions to compute a broad suite of clinical and
    research biomarkers from routine data. Implemented measures include
    metabolic indices of insulin sensitivity and resistance (fasting, oral
    glucose tolerance test, adipose, tracer or DXA based), lipid markers,
    liver steatosis and fibrosis scores, anthropometric z-scores, obesity
    indices, cardiovascular risk scores and blood pressure indices, psychiatric risk scores,
    pulmonary function measures, biomarker panels from alternate biofluids (urine, saliva, sweat).
    All calculations can be accessed through a unified 'all_health_markers()' dispatcher function.
